```esql
FROM employees
| EVAL Ks = salary / 1000 // thousands
| STATS under_40K = COUNT(*) WHERE Ks < 40,
        inbetween = COUNT(*) WHERE 40 <= Ks AND Ks < 60,
        over_60K  = COUNT(*) WHERE 60 <= Ks,
        total     = COUNT(*)
```

| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 36 | 39 | 25 | 100 |
